snippet.title: DRAGON BALL FighterZ - Launch Trailer | PS4, X1, PC
snippet.description:
Let's hurry up and get this started! Get ready to experience the next level of fighting games on January 26. Join Goku, Piccolo, Vegeta and the rest of the squad as they take on a mysterious new foe, Android 21. DRAGON BALL FighterZ launches on January 26 for Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC via Steam. Pre-order your copy while there's still time: http://bit.ly/FighterZ
